graph TD
    A[BenchmarkPipeline] --> B["Iterate target; model pairs"]
    B --> C[BacktestPipeline]
    C -->|Forecast outputs| D[EvaluationPipeline]
    D -->|Evaluation reports| E[AnalysisPipeline]
    F[(Target and Model List)] --> A
    C --> G[Generate Forecasts]
    D --> H[Compute Metrics]
